| If you see... | Use this command first | Why? |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **CrashLoopBackOff** | `kubectl logs` | To see the Java exception/error message. |
| **ImagePullBackOff** | `kubectl describe` | To see if the error is a 404 (wrong name) or 401 (auth error). |
| **"App is running but can't find a file"** | `kubectl exec` | To manually check if the file exists in the folder. |
| **Pending Status** | `kubectl describe` | To see if your cluster is out of CPU or RAM. |

